data.description: Escape the city hustle and embrace the serenity of this gorgeous home located on a generous 3.9 acre parcel and includes a tranquil pond for fishing or just relaxing. Nestled at the end of a peaceful dead-end road, this property offers a perfect blend of modern comfort and natural beauty.  Home is located only 2.5 miles from I-65 and was completely renovated in 2020 with a new LVP flooring, updated kitchen with new stainless steel appliances and quartz counter top, new hot water heater, new decks and new landscaping.  The detached 2 car garage is also plumbed for a bathroom.
